article.headline: Miami (Ohio) 72, Oakland, Mich. 46
article.story: OXFORD, Ohio (AP) -- Nathan Peavy scored 16 points and grabbed nine rebounds Sunday to lead Miami of Ohio to a 72-46 win over Oakland University. Alex Moosmann scored 13 and Tim Pollitz added 10 for Miami (4-6), which shot 50 percent from the floor and never trailed. Miami took advantage of Oakland's miscues, scoring 25 points on 17 turnovers by the Golden Grizzlies (6-5). Vova Severovas and Derick Nelson each scored 13 points for Oakland, which shot 36 percent and was outscored 36-18 in the paint.
